These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
4 different pets are kept: hamster, goldfish, fish, snake
1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
5. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | juice | sprite | hot-chocolate | almond-milk |
| Pet        | hamster | goldfish   | snake | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, western, mystery, documentary
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, indian, egyptian, argentine
1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the egyptian##1
3. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
4. the mexican is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the indian is on the right of the egyptian##1
6. the mexican is the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | thriller  | western  | documentary |
| Nationality   | argentine    | mexican | egyptian | indian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, plum, potato, cucumber
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, thriller, family, satire
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
2. the person eating potato is in an even position##4
3. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
4. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | cucumber | potato | plum    | cherry      |
| Movie-Genre   | family        | satire     | epic | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, board-games, sudoku, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, pop, rock, electronic
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the fan of salsa and the fan of electronic##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the fan of rock is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | video-games | card-games | board-games | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | salsa   | pop    | electronic  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, classical, d&b, reggae
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, colombian, egyptian, argentine
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the argentine##1
2. the colombian is the fan of reggae##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
5. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4
6. the italian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | dubstep    | d&b   | reggae       |
| Nationality   | italian | argentine | egyptian | colombian |

