2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person watching satire movies##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
6. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy | action | sports    |
| Transport     | jet-ski | bus  | scooter     | tram |

