.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, architect, freelancer, photographer
4 different pets are kept: turtle, cat, ferret, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the architect##3
2. the photographer is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the photographer##3
4. the photographer is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the writer is between the photographer and the architect##2
6. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the cat is between the writer and the owner of the ferret##2
8. the writer is on the left or right of the architect##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | architect | writer      | photographer | freelancer |
| Pet   | turtle  | chinchilla | cat    | ferret            |

