.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, 7up, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, r&b, blues, techno
1. the person drinking fanta is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the fan of techno is between the fan of ambient and the person drinking 7up##2
4. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
6. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea       | 7up   | fanta | water |
| Music-Genre   | blues | r&b | techno        | ambient    |

