.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola, almond-milk, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, golf, handball, baseball
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | sprite   | cola      | almond-milk      |
| Sport      | golf | handball | baseball | ice-hockey |

