2. the fan of folk is in an even position##4
3. the person eating peach is in an even position##4
4. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
5. the person eating grapes is between the fan of classical and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | artichoke | peach  | grapes  | cucumber |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | folk | funk | classical   |

