.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, rock-climbing, baking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, sailing, lacrosse, rugby
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | baking | gardening         | card-games   | rock-climbing |
| Sport   | lacrosse    | sailing | rugby | cricket   |

