2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
5. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | cooking | singing | baking    | video-games |
| Sport   | swimming   | sailing  | parkour | snowboarding     |

