.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, collecting, rock-climbing, puzzles
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, polish, brazilian
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
3. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the polish is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
5. the egyptian is between the brazilian and the polish##2
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | rock-climbing | fishing | collecting    |
| Nationality   | polish | egyptian  | brazilian     | chinese |

