.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, almond-milk, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: orange, tomato, blueberry, plum
1. the person eating tomato is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating plum##1
5. the person eating plum is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person eating blueberry is in an even position##4
7. the person eating orange is the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | hot-chocolate    | almond-milk       | lemonade |
| Food       | tomato  | blueberry | plum | orange  |

