.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, egyptian, russian, brazilian
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, roller, scooter, taxi
1. the german is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the russian##1
5. the german is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | egyptian | russian | german  | brazilian |
| Transport     | snowmobile      | scooter       | roller | taxi     |

