.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, firefighter, photographer, doctor
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, bike, bus, car
1. the firefighter is in an even position##4
2. the firefighter is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
3. the person driving the bike is between the accountant and the person driving the roller##2
4. the firefighter is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the doctor##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | accountant | photographer   | doctor | firefighter |
| Transport   | car          | bike | roller         | bus  |

 